item.title: Klein-Backed SPAC, Quantum Firm Infleqtion Ink $1.8 Billion Deal
item.description: Quantum computing firm Infleqtion has agreed to merge with a blank-check firm led by Michael Klein in a pact that gives the startup a pre-money valuation of $1.8 billion.
